## Validation Rules

| Rule                     | Condition                                              | Error Message                                             |
| ------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------ | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| Duplicate PAN            | Same PAN already exists in system                      | "A customer with this PAN already exists."                |
| Duplicate GST            | Same GST already exists in system                      | "A customer with this GST already exists."                |
| GST State Code required  | GST Number entered but GST State Code is blank         | "Please select the GST state code."                       |
| Lead already converted   | Selected Lead ID is already linked to a Customer       | "This lead has already been converted to a customer."     |
| Mandatory fields blank   | Any field marked * is empty on Save                    | Inline red error below each field                         |

---

## Post-Save System Behaviors

| Trigger                | System Action                                                           |
| ---------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Customer Saved         | Auto-generates Customer ID (CUST-YYYY-SEQ)                              |
| Imported from Lead     | Lead status updated to "Converted"; linked Lead ID stored on customer   |
| Primary Site           | Site record created and linked to customer (Site ID auto-generated)     |
| Audit Log              | Records creation timestamp, user, and source (Lead import / Manual)     |

